    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A term referring to the social relationship of a group, rather than its territorial demarcation, in regard to its support of community life in each tlaxilacalli (neighborhood) of Mexico-Tenochtitlan.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000320/GRI-FloCo</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000109721/GRI, FloCo terminology (2019-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Un término que se refiere a la relación social de un grupo, más que a su demarcación territorial, en lo que respecta a su apoyo a la vida comunitaria en cada tlaxilacalli (barrio) de México-Tenochtitlan.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000320/GRI-FloCo</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000109721/GRI, FloCo terminology (2019-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tlahtolli tlen quimanextia queniuhcatza pan ce altepetzin macehualmeh moxeloah ica grupos, maz que ce nezcayotilli tlen tlalli campa itztoqueh, tlen campa inintlapalehuiliz pan ininnemiliz altepetzitzin pan cehcen tlaxilacalli tlen Mexco-Tenochtitlan.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000320/GRI-FloCo</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000109721/GRI, FloCo terminology (2019-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
